videos.description: Q1 (2:39) MISS Madinah Muhammad with the step-through move, knocks in the layup.

videos.headline: K. Sessions made Three Point Jumper.

videos.description: Q1 (1:29) MISS Madinah Muhammad, with a defenders hand in her face, sinks a three point jumper. Assisted by Shandricka Sessom.
videos.headline: M. Muhammad, with a defenders hand in her face, sinks a three point jumper. Assisted by S. Sessom.

videos.description: Q2 (9:52) MISS Madinah Muhammad on fire, sinks a jumper to start off the second quarter.

videos.description: Q2 (4:26) SCAR A'ja Wilson made layup. Great pass by Asia Dozier.
videos.headline: A. Wilson made Layup. Great pass by A. Dozier.

videos.description: Q2 (4:02) SCAR A'ja Wilson grabs the defensive rebound, lobs it long to Tiffany Mitchell on the run who finishes the layup with ease.
videos.headline: A. Wilson grabs the defensive rebound, lobs it long to T. Mitchell on the run who finishes the layup with ease.

videos.description: Q2 (2:38) MISS A'Queen Hayes gets in front of the pass to make the steal, gets back down on the other end to make the driving layup.
videos.headline: A. Hayes gets in front of the pass to make the steal, gets back down on the other end to make the driving layup.
